### 📦 Create a post
POST http://localhost:5000/api/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Enjoying the sunset 🌅 #goodvibes",
  "media": [
    { "url": "https://cdn.app.com/photos/sunset.jpg", "type": "image" }
  ]
}

### 🌍 Get all public posts (feed) — first page
GET http://localhost:5000/api/posts?limit=4
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 🌍 Get next page (pass the last post’s createdAt ISO string as cursor)
@cursor = 2025-10-30T14:22:09.000Z

GET http://localhost:5000/api/posts?limit=10&cursor={{cursor}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 🔍 Get a single post by ID
@postId = a49af298-a8f4-4558-a31a-a15f25b50b3b

GET http://localhost:5000/api/posts/{{postId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ❤️ Like a post
POST http://localhost:5000/api/posts/{{postId}}/like
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 💔 Unlike a post
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/posts/{{postId}}/like
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 💬 Comment on a post
POST http://localhost:5000/api/posts/{{postId}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "This looks amazing! 😍"
}

###

### 🗑️ Delete a post (only by author)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/posts/{{postId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ✏️ Edit a post
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/posts/{{postId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Updated my post — feeling even more positive today! 🌞"
}

### 👤 Get all posts by a specific user
@targetUserId = a274db80-a8f5-47ad-b7a2-6cc2d82eae93

GET http://localhost:5000/api/posts/user/{{targetUserId}}?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 📄 Next page (with cursor)
@cursor = 2025-10-30T14:22:09.000Z

GET http://localhost:5000/api/posts/user/{{targetUserId}}?limit=5&cursor={{cursor}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
